{"tid":1588292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［外媒］大家養成呢個習慣","createTime":"2019-09-22T17:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T18:43:29.000Z","uid":312412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9dad691a2684733479ff0b84d3087946798149","tid":1588292,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"頭盔：我只係一個垃圾p牌和理非，有錯求屌醒<br />\n<br />\n求求大家每日都上Twitter推一推下d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係發完夢有新聞之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推下BBC, Time, The New York Times呢d，但記住係英文版唔好follow中文版，中文版係殘體比5毛睇推泥都哂時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我見Twitter d post 得嗰幾百個retweet連一千都冇，當初唔係有二百萬個手足架咩，就算係冷氣軍師都幫下手丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有一日見到每個香港post都過萬retweets<br />\n<br />\n最後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b35c14bb65a7873f2fc962741e5a6eb4fa1a1efe","tid":1588292,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"8e10e9678231e124182c7c1ba5a7d6646b5f637f","tid":1588292,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:43:29.000Z","msg":"每日12點, 幫手整個在twitter 要推的list 出黎得唔得?<br />\n一出list, 各位手足各自開工,<br />\n係twitter 又好, Quora 又好, Reddit 又好, 總之有咁遠同我散咁遠<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得唔得?</span></span></strong>"}]}